sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case TC_001_CSMS: Cold Boot Charge Point
    Note over CP,CS: OCPP 1.6j - Chapter 3.1

    CP->>CS: BootNotification.req
    Note right of CP: chargePointVendor, chargePointModel, etc.

    CS-->>CP: BootNotification.conf
    Note over CS: Validation: status MUST be "Accepted"
    Note left of CS: status = Accepted, interval = x seconds, currentTime

    loop For each connector (including connectorId=0)
        CP->>CS: StatusNotification.req
        Note right of CP: connectorId, status = Available, errorCode = NoError
        CS-->>CP: StatusNotification.conf
    end

    Note over CP,CS: Validation: StatusNotification.req status MUST be "Available"

    loop Every x seconds (interval from BootNotification.conf)
        CP->>CS: Heartbeat.req
        CS-->>CP: Heartbeat.conf
        Note left of CS: currentTime
    end

    Note over CP,CS: Validation: Heartbeat interval must equal interval from BootNotification.conf
